OL,5, An expert witness was asked by a Post  
OL,6, Office prosecutor to consider changing 
OL,7, his testimony to avoid a "damaging     
OL,8, concession", the BBC has found.        
OL,10,FFujitsu engineer Gareth Jenkins        
OL,11,Frephrased parts of a report on the     
OL,12,FHorizon IT system after advice from    
OL,13,Fbarrister Warwick Tatford.             
OL,15,FThe evidence was used in the 2010 case 
OL,16,Fagainst postmistress Seema Misra, who  
OL,17,Fwas wrongly jailed while pregnant.     
OL,19,FThe Post Office has said it is "focused
OL,20,Fon righting the wrongs of the past".   
